org.nlpcraft.model.builder

Class NCModelDescriptorBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nlpcraft.model.builder.NCModelDescriptorBuilder

  • public class NCModelDescriptorBuilder
extends Object
    Model descriptor builder for NCModelDescriptor instances.

    To use this builder start by invoking one of the following static method to create new builder instance:
    • newDescriptor(String, String, String)
    • newDescriptor()
    Once you have the builder instance you can set all necessary properties and finally call build() method to get properly constructed NCModelDescriptor instance.
